creator: Home Warranty of America
descriptionHtml:
At Home Warranty of America, we understand that your home is your most important asset. Equipment and appliance breakdowns are stressful – and expensive.

Our business is built on helping homeowners protect their homes and their budgets with simple, reliable solutions. Our home warranties offer great value and security. Our customers know that when a covered appliance breaks down, we'll be there to help. Homeowners can request service 24/7, 365 days a year through our website, or by calling our customer service team.

We know each home is unique, and we offer a range of plans and options to achieve the coverage that's right for you. Whether you're buying or selling a home, or want protection for your existing home, we can help.
descriptionShort: Helping homeowners protect their homes with simple, reliable solutions.
